    • Method Detail

      • getPAMParam

        public String getPAMParam(String name,
                          String cfgName,
                          String def)
        Try to find the configuration in the following order:
        • Local configuration stored in this XWikiPAMConfig instance (pam_*name*)
        • XWiki Preferences page (pam_*name*)
        • xwiki.cfg configuration file (pam.*name*)
        • A final configuration that could be overriden by extended authenticators
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the property in XWikiPreferences.
        cfgName - the name of the property in xwiki.cfg.
        def - default value.
        Returns:
        the value of the property.
        Since:
        9.1.1

      • getPAMParam

        public String getPAMParam(String name,

        the value of the property.
